text: The Fiat Ulysse was a large car with seven seats made by Fiat in two generations between 1994 and 2010. It is the only Eurovan in the PSA/Fiat joint vesture to have retained the same name in the second generation. == First generation (1994−2002) == === Engines === * 1.8 73 kW (99 hp) * 2.0 89 kW (121 hp) * 2.0 16V 97 kW (132 hp) and 100 kW (136 hp) * 2.0 Turbo 108 kW (147 hp) * 1.9 TD 66 kW (90 hp) * 2.0 JTD 80 kW (109 hp) * 2.1 TD 80 kW (109 hp) == Second generation (2002−2010) == === Engines === * 2.0 16V 100 kW (136 hp) * 3.0 V6 152 kW (207 hp) * 2.0 JTD 80 kW (109 hp), 88 kW (120 hp) and 100 kW (136 hp) * 2.2 JTD 94 kW (128 hp) and 125 kW (170 hp) Ulysse Category:1990s automobiles Category:2000s automobiles Category:2010s automobiles Category:Front wheel drive vehicles
title: Fiat Ulysse
